---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About Author - Quasar Contact"
  description="Learn about Artem Turlenko, the creator of Quasar Contact secure messaging platform."
>
<div class="main-content page-content">
  <div class="container inner">
    <div class="page-header">
      <h2>About the Author</h2>
      <p class="page-subtitle">Meet the creator behind Quasar Contact</p>
    </div>

    <div class="author-content">
      <div class="author-intro">
        <div class="author-avatar">
          <div class="avatar-placeholder">
            <svg
              width="80"
              height="80"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="1.5"
            >
              <path d="M20 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H8a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2" />
              <circle cx="12" cy="7" r="4" />
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="author-info">
          <h2>Artem Turlenko</h2>
        
          <p class="author-title">
            Software Developer | Full-Stack Enthusiast | UI/UX Designer
          </p>
          <p class="author-location">üìç Germany, Essen</p>
        </div>
      </div>



      <div class="content-section">
        <h3>My Background</h3>
        <p>
          With extensive experience in modern web technologies including
          Angular, Node.js, and real-time communication systems, I've
          dedicated my career to building secure, user-friendly
          applications. My expertise spans frontend development, backend
          architecture, encryption implementation, and database design.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="content-section">
        <h3>Why Quasar Contact?</h3>
        <p>
          In today's digital landscape, privacy is becoming increasingly
          rare. I built Quasar Contact to address this challenge - creating
          a messaging platform that puts user privacy first, implements true
          end-to-end encryption, and maintains a zero-knowledge
          architecture. Every technical decision is made with user privacy
          and security in mind.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="content-section">
        <h3>Technical Expertise</h3>
        <div class="skills-grid">
          <div class="skill-category">
            <h4>Frontend</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>Angular 18+</li>
              <li>TypeScript</li>
              <li>RxJS</li>
              <li>Progressive Web Apps</li>
              <li>Web Crypto API</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="skill-category">
            <h4>Backend</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>Node.js</li>
              <li>Express.js</li>
              <li>Socket.IO</li>
              <li>MongoDB</li>
              <li>JWT Authentication</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="skill-category">
            <h4>Security</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>End-to-End Encryption</li>
              <li>Zero-Knowledge Architecture</li>
              <li>GDPR Compliance</li>
              <li>Security Best Practices</li>
              <li>Privacy by Design</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="content-section">
        <h3>Philosophy</h3>
        <p>I believe that:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <strong>Privacy is a fundamental right</strong> - Not a luxury
            or optional feature
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Security should be transparent</strong> - Users should
            understand how their data is protected
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Technology should empower users</strong> - Not exploit
            or surveillance them
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Open communication fosters innovation</strong> -
            Feedback and collaboration improve everything
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="content-section">
        <h3>Future Vision</h3>
        <p>
          My goal is to continuously improve Quasar Contact based on user
          feedback and evolving security needs. I'm committed to maintaining
          the highest standards of privacy and security while making the
          platform accessible to users of all technical backgrounds.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="contact-section">
        <h3>Get in Touch</h3>
        <p>
          I'm always open to feedback, suggestions, and discussions about
          privacy, security, or technology in general.
        </p>

        <div class="contact-links">
          <a
            href="mailto:artem.turlenko@quasar.contact"
            class="contact-link"
          >
            <svg
              width="20"
              height="20"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2"
            >
              <path d="m4 4 7.07 17 2.51-7.39 7.39-2.51L4 4z" />
            </svg>
            artem.turlenko@quasar.contact
          </a>
          <a href="https://github.com/art2url" class="contact-link">
            <svg
              width="20"
              height="20"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="currentColor"
            >
              <path
                d="M12 0c-6.626 0-12 5.373-12 12 0 5.302 3.438 9.8 8.207 11.387.599.111.793-.261.793-.577v-2.234c-3.338.726-4.033-1.416-4.033-1.416-.546-1.387-1.333-1.756-1.333-1.756-1.089-.745.083-.729.083-.729 1.205.084 1.839 1.237 1.839 1.237 1.07 1.834 2.807 1.304 3.492.997.107-.775.418-1.305.762-1.604-2.665-.305-5.467-1.334-5.467-5.931 0-1.311.469-2.381 1.236-3.221-.124-.303-.535-1.524.117-3.176 0 0 1.008-.322 3.301 1.23.957-.266 1.983-.399 3.003-.404 1.02.005 2.047.138 3.006.404 2.291-1.552 3.297-1.23 3.297-1.23.653 1.653.242 2.874.118 3.176.77.84 1.235 1.911 1.235 3.221 0 4.609-2.807 5.624-5.479 5.921.43.372.823 1.102.823 2.222v3.293c0 .319.192.694.801.576 4.765-1.589 8.199-6.086 8.199-11.386 0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12z"
              />
            </svg>
            GitHub Profile
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="security-contact">
          <h4>üîí Security Issues</h4>
          <p>For security vulnerabilities or concerns, please contact:</p>
          <a
            href="mailto:artem.turlenko@quasar.contact"
            class="security-email"
            >artem.turlenko@quasar.contact</a
          >
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>
</BaseLayout>